B’e '''àite-coise''' earrann rathaid le stiallan geala oirre airson luchd-coiseachd a dhol tarsainn.

Tha ceithir seòrsaichean ann an RA:
* Pegasus Crossing (each)
* Pelican Crossing
* Puffin Crossing
* Toucan Crossing
* Zebra Crossing

Far a bheil clann-sgoile a’ dol tarsainn an rathaid, bidh fear- neo tè-lollipop ann.

